commit.message:
fix: '''\ and """\ being incorrectly detected (#149)

The \ after ''' and """ is not a line break. It is used to disable the
leading linebreak in multiline strings

Fixes #138

Co-authored-by: Leonidas Loucas <lloucas@purestorage.com>
